@startuml
actor "Event Organizer" as Organizer
participant "UI (Thymeleaf)" as UI
participant "API Gateway\n(:8080)" as Gateway
participant "Event Controller" as Controller
participant "Event Service" as Service
participant "Event Repository" as Repository
database "Event DB\n(PostgreSQL)" as DB

Organizer -> UI: Fill event form & submit
UI -> Gateway: POST /api/events\n(JWT in Authorization header)
activate Gateway

Gateway -> Gateway: Validate JWT token
Gateway -> Controller: POST /api/events
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: createEvent(EventDTO)
activate Service

Service -> Repository: save(Event)
activate Repository

Repository -> DB: INSERT INTO events...
activate DB
DB --> Repository: Event entity
deactivate DB

Repository --> Service: saved Event
deactivate Repository

Service --> Controller: EventResponseDTO
deactivate Service

Controller --> Gateway: 201 Created
deactivate Controller

Gateway --> UI: JSON response
deactivate Gateway

UI --> Organizer: Show success page
@enduml
